snippet.title: Best VGM 674 - Yoshi's Story - On The Beach
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 2248 - https://youtu.be/K_qt3fBYD8M

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo 64
Yoshi's Story (1998)
On The Beach
Kazumi Totaka
